==English==

===Etymology===
Recorded since 1591, from {{der|en|LL.|polygamia}}, from {{der|en|grc|πολυγαμία}}, itself from {{m|grc|πολύγαμος|t=married to many}}, from {{m|grc|πολύς|t=many}} + {{m|grc|γάμος|t=marriage}}. Relates to modern prefix and suffix {{af|en|poly-|-gamy}}.

